OL,3,CNew football regulator must 'be based
OL,4,Cwhere sport is woven into fabric'
OL,6,FA town which saw its football club
OL,7,Fdisbanded after financial issues
OL,8,Fshould be the base for the sport's
OL,9,Fproposed new regulator, its MPs have
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FBury FC were kicked out of the
OL,13,FFootball League in 2019 after a
OL,14,Ftakeover bid collapsed, leaving the
OL,15,Fclub heavily in debt and sparking
OL,16,Fcalls for a regulator to make sure
OL,17,Fteams are being run properly.
