OL,4,Cwhere sport is woven into fabric'
OL,6,F"In Bury we've the resolve and
OL,7,Fdetermination you should expect from
OL,8,Fthis new regulator in its quest to
OL,9,Fprotect the beautiful game now and in
OL,10,Fthe future."
OL,12,FAn independent regulator was the key
OL,13,Frecommendation of the 2021 fan-led
OL,14,Freview of football - which led to the
OL,15,FFootball Governance Bill -
OL,16,Fcommissioned by the Conservative
OL,17,FGovernment in the wake of the European
OL,18,FSuper League scandal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
