OL,6,FIts progress through Parliament was
OL,7,Finterrupted when the General Election
OL,8,Fwas called in summer 2024, but the new
OL,9,FLabour Government has picked up the
OL,10,Fbaton.
OL,12,FOne of the regulator's key early tasks
OL,13,Fwill be to produce a 'State of the
OL,14,FGame' review examining football's
OL,15,Ffinancial flows, including the
OL,16,Fcontroversial parachute payments made
OL,17,Fto clubs relegated from the Premier
OL,18,FLeague.
