OL,6,FThe bill is back in the House of
OL,7,FCommons after it cleared the House of
OL,8,FLords in March on its journey to
OL,9,Fbecoming law.
OL,11,FLiverpool West Derby Labour MP Ian
OL,12,FByrne said the football regulator
OL,13,Fshould have a role in setting ticket
OL,14,Fprices as top-flight games are often
OL,15,Ftoo expensive for working class
OL,16,Fsupporters to go.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
