OL,6,FMr Byrne said: "We need to tackle the
OL,7,Fissue of the pricing out of working
OL,8,Fclass supporters. For 2025/26, of
OL,9,Fthose announced, the majority of
OL,10,Fprices have been frozen at Premier
OL,11,FLeague clubs, but it has only happened
OL,12,Ffollowing the concerted and
OL,13,Fcoordinated efforts by fan groups led
OL,14,Fby the FSA (Football Supporters'
OL,15,FAssociation)."
