OL,6,FHe added: "The reality is that prices
OL,7,Fare far too high already, especially
OL,8,Ffor younger fans. I witnessed
OL,9,Fthousands of working class supporters,
OL,10,Fyoung working class supporters priced
OL,11,Fout of Anfield yesterday with some
OL,12,Ftickets going for over #1,000."
OL,14,FHe told MPs he was concerned about a
OL,15,Fdecreasing number of season tickets on
OL,16,Fsale by top flight clubs.
