OL,6,FMr Byrne continued: "Therefore I ask
OL,7,Fthe Secretary of State to consider the
OL,8,Ffollowing amendments. That the
OL,9,Findependent football regulator has
OL,10,Finvolvement in ticket pricing
OL,11,Fincluding reporting on this activity
OL,12,Fin its state of football report, and
OL,13,Fensuring that fans have genuine input
OL,14,Finto their club's ticketing policy
OL,15,Fthrough structured engagement it'll
OL,16,Foversee."
