OL,6,FHe added that the football regulator
OL,7,Fshould also review concession prices,
OL,8,Ffor younger and older fans to ensure
OL,9,Fthey aren't unable to afford to go to
OL,10,Fgames. Mr Byrne said: "We cannot allow
OL,11,Fthe greed of some owners with no idea
OL,12,Fof how important working class game is
OL,13,Fto the very communities that it should
OL,14,Falways serve."
