OL,6,FAnd ministers indicated the regulator
OL,7,Fcould eventually be expanded to
OL,8,Finclude women's football.
OL,10,FDavid Kogan has been selected as the
OL,11,FGovernment's preferred candidate to
OL,12,Fchair the new regulator.
OL,14,FKogan, who has previously advised the
OL,15,FPremier League and the EFL on
OL,16,Ftelevision rights deals in a 45-year
OL,17,Fcareer as a media executive, business
OL,18,Fleader and corporate advisor, is now
OL,19,Fset to head up the watchdog intended
OL,20,Fto ensure football clubs in the top
OL,21,Ffive tiers are financially sustainable.
